<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p3.itc.cn/images01/20200810/753c107ab24c4f7db7d79208a6fd380e.jpeg" max-width="600"><span class="img-desc" style="font-size: 16px;">许家印视察恒大汽车生产基地涂装车间</span></img></p>
